  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dc5\u0db6\u0da9 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One killed in coastal shooting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Nihal Talduwa, Police Media Spokesman, said that a person was killed in a shooting by two unknown persons who came on a motorcycle at the Vivekananda Kanda Road area of \u200b\u200bKoorah Bada last night (30th).",
        "The dead are Sundaram Antony Bernard, 51, a broker and moneylender who lived in the same area.",
        "He was shot in the head and chest area by a 9 mm firearm. The spokesperson added that he died while being taken to the hospital.",
        "The reason for the shooting has not yet been revealed. Coastal Police are investigating."
      ],
